{
  "stem": "16.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And imagine, 2,000 people-- at least 2,000 people running towards that one American soldier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I would have kissed his ass, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I just couldn't get close enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And within minutes, it was swarming with Americans, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they were holding us back from beating up on the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because some of them picked up the, the guns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And with the butt, they started hitting the Germans that just tore off their ranks, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were-- they were saving their lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, about a couple hours later, a major makes an announcement in English, in Yiddish, in a couple other languages, that you are free now.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You are welcome to stay here as long as you want to beef up your, your appearance, in other words, to get yourself back into shape.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The kitchen will be open 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You can eat all the time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But don't eat more than every two hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You can eat a little bit every two hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If you eat too much, you're going to get sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And you can die.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And some of them did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because wouldn't listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They couldn't stop themselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They died of dysentery.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was at a-- at a-- I think we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It must have been a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- it wasn't the same kind of barracks that we were sleeping in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It must've been the German camp, or wherever-- wherever the German soldiers were, were living.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is about 3 kilometers outside of Munich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was building myself up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I ate every two hours.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean at 2 o'clock in the morning, at 4 o'clock in the morning, at 6:00 in the morning-- every two hours, just a little bit, remembering what the major told me.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
